  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00767', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Berry所提出的文化適應模式中，移民者專注於適應新環境，只和主流文化建立關係，同時刻意拒絕自己 原本的文化和傳統，這是下列那一種應對方式？', '["邊緣化", "隔離", "同化", "整合"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00768', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '身心障礙者就醫過程中，常會因各種因素而遇到阻礙，若因一些不被尊重、疏忽或貶抑等經驗之故，造 成不信任醫療服務提供者，這是下列那一種面向的就醫障礙？', '["態度", "表達意見", "資訊不對稱", "協調"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00769', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若刑事被告或犯罪嫌疑人因精神障礙或其他心智缺陷無法為完全之陳述時，地方主管機關可聲請法院同 意指派社會工作人員擔任下列何種協助角色？', '["法定代理人", "出庭輔導人", "權利保障人", "訴訟輔佐人"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00770', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一般而言，身心障礙福利的政策模式，可分為社會福利與公民權利兩種模式，下列對於公民權利模式的 敘述何者正確？', '["障礙是社會排除的後果，而非個人身心缺陷的結果", "障礙意謂著缺陷，故個人無法以慣常的方式在社會上工作或生活", "障礙者的社會生活需求，必須以另外的管道來解決", "身障福利的取得基於資格認定而非法律保障"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00771', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '評估兒童及少年的權益與福祉時，生態系統是常被應用的理論，下列那一項說明並不是以生態系統來評 估兒童及少年的權益與福祉？', '["評估時需考量兒童及少年的家庭所處的外部及鉅視系統", "辨識環境中的不利因素是評估時的重點之一", "界定遭遇困難的兒童及少年為問題的來源", "評估是一個過程而不是一個事件"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00772', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一項是關於兒少受虐的錯誤認知？', '["兒少受虐現象存在於各種社經背景的家庭中", "會虐待兒少者對所有人都會暴力相向", "男孩也可能是性虐待的受害者", "疏忽是兒少虐待的類型之一"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
